name: Agog 11 Crazy Scan Colour Shiny
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture photogrammetry scan in nature, revelling in the imperfection of artifacts. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
